- Okay.

298
00:23:06,010 --> 00:23:08,428
Hey, you were late
this morning too, right?

299
00:23:08,429 --> 00:23:10,264
I'm not you. I came back from court.

300
00:23:10,973 --> 00:23:13,057
- Really?
- How are you always late?

301
00:23:13,058 --> 00:23:15,351
Know how early I left?
I had a morning meeting--

302
00:23:15,352 --> 00:23:17,937
