304
00:23:21,025 --> 00:23:22,358
It's just a suggestion.

305
00:23:22,359 --> 00:23:25,320
And you guys don't clock in. It's just us.

306
00:23:25,321 --> 00:23:27,489
- Hey, they raised the price here.
- What?

307
00:23:31,368 --> 00:23:34,662
