Things have really improved.

313
00:23:48,677 --> 00:23:52,222
No, I meant I'll pay out of pocket.
My treat.

314
00:23:52,765 --> 00:23:54,223
It's not about money for me.

315
00:23:54,224 --> 00:23:55,476
Yeah, it is.

316
00:23:55,601 --> 00:23:57,477
- You're right.
- You're unbelievable.

317
00:23:57,478 --> 00:24:00,021
