- Finish this first.
- I'm going to finish it.

322
00:24:18,707 --> 00:24:21,126
Happy now?
More radish kimchi, please. We're out.

323
00:24:31,136 --> 00:24:32,346
I already want to go home.

324
00:24:36,809 --> 00:24:38,601
You're such an old man.

325
00:24:38,602 --> 00:24:39,936
Is that scorched rice tea?

326
00:24:39,937 --> 00:24:41,020
Thank you.

327
00:24:41,021 --> 00:24:43,690
You're the weirdos with iced coffee
in this cold weather.

328
00:24:43,691 --> 00:24:45,025
You'll end up frozen stiff.

329
00:24:47,277 --> 00:24:48,529
What are you drinking?

330
00:24:49,029 --> 00:24:50,363
A strawberry yogurt smoothie.

331
00:24:50,364 --> 00:24:52,490
It really doesn't suit you.
Don't drink that.

332
00:24:52,491 --> 00:24:54,993
Don't force your coffee down.

333
00:24:54,994 --> 00:24:56,285
That's tricking your body.

334
00:24:56,286 --> 00:24:57,830
Should I call you old too?

335
00:24:59,498 --> 00:25:00,790
I just write it here?

336
00:25:00,791 --> 00:25:03,626
- What is he up to?
- What if they don't drop the charges?

337
00:25:03,627 --> 00:25:06,462
You have to trust me,
or we can't reach a deal!

338
00:25:06,463 --> 00:25:07,839
Gosh, it's so simple.

339
00:25:07,840 --> 00:25:10,133
You're doing it again. Just sit still.

340
00:25:10,134 --> 00:25:12,802
Everyone's an attorney here. Sit still.

341
00:25:12,803 --> 00:25:14,012
Hey, Changwon.

342
00:25:14,013 --> 00:25:17,306
I don't get how someone
this scatterbrained aced the CSAT.

343
00:25:17,307 --> 00:25:20,935
That's why I barely passed the bar
after using up all five tries.

344
00:25:20,936 --> 00:25:23,480
