Our friend Changwon did so well--

345
00:25:26,025 --> 00:25:27,026
Chief.

346
00:25:28,152 --> 00:25:29,819
Yes, how are you?

347
00:25:29,820 --> 00:25:31,362
I hate that capitalist smile.

348
00:25:31,363 --> 00:25:34,366
