374
00:26:39,556 --> 00:26:40,848
Beat the odds to win big.

375
00:26:40,849 --> 00:26:43,184
There she goes again,
like a moth to the flame.

376
00:26:43,185 --> 00:26:44,769
Seriously,

377
00:26:44,770 --> 00:26:47,480
