404
00:28:40,260 --> 00:28:43,137
Come on, is it that hard
to knock a little off the fee?

405
00:28:43,138 --> 00:28:45,807
Why do you keep messing with me?

406
00:28:49,394 --> 00:28:52,773
<i>I instinctively tried to call for help,
but my phone didn't work.</i>

407
00:28:54,316 --> 00:28:56,400
<i>So I ran to the landline in the office</i>

408
00:28:56,401 --> 00:28:58,570
<i>and picked up the receiver
to call the police,</i>

409
00:28:59,321 --> 00:29:01,698
<i>but he threw it away.</i>

410
00:29:03,867 --> 00:29:06,328
