494
00:35:49,606 --> 00:35:50,939
I had so much fun today.

495
00:35:50,940 --> 00:35:52,233
Me too.

496
00:35:52,817 --> 00:35:54,110
We didn't get to talk much.

497
00:35:54,694 --> 00:35:55,903
It's such a shame.

498
00:35:55,904 --> 00:35:58,405
Yeah. I'll be in touch again.

499
00:35:58,406 --> 00:36:01,576
- Yes, please make sure you do.
